# Testing & QA Master Skill
**Version:** 2.0.0  
**Type:** Self-Improving | Test-Driven | Quality-Focused

## Core Purpose
Implement comprehensive testing strategies including unit tests, integration tests, E2E tests, performance tests, and test automation with intelligent coverage optimization.

## Self-Improvement Engine
```yaml
learning_system:
  - Track test execution patterns
  - Learn from test failures
  - Adapt test coverage based on bugs
  - Optimize test suite performance
  - Remember flaky test patterns
```

